# ESP-IDF 5.5 Compatibility Configuration
# This file contains mappings for deprecated config options

# Removed options that no longer exist in ESP-IDF 5.5:
# - CONFIG_HEAP_CORRUPTION_DETECTION (use HEAP_POISONING instead)
# - CONFIG_FREERTOS_ASSERT_ON_UNTESTED_FUNCTION (removed)
# - CONFIG_FREERTOS_ASSERT_FAIL_ABORT (use CONFIG_FREERTOS_ASSERT)
# - CONFIG_ESP_COREDUMP_* options (restructured in 5.x)

# Task watchdog was renamed
# Old: CONFIG_ESP_TASK_WDT
# New: CONFIG_ESP_TASK_WDT_INIT

# These options should NOT be set in sdkconfig files for ESP-IDF 5.5:
# CONFIG_HEAP_CORRUPTION_DETECTION
# CONFIG_FREERTOS_ASSERT_ON_UNTESTED_FUNCTION
# CONFIG_FREERTOS_ASSERT_FAIL_ABORT
# CONFIG_ESP_COREDUMP_ENABLE_TO_FLASH
# CONFIG_ESP_COREDUMP_DATA_FORMAT_ELF
# CONFIG_ESP_COREDUMP_CHECKSUM_CRC32
# CONFIG_ESP_COREDUMP_MAX_TASKS_NUM